{"tid":986628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★大橋新春將迎海量人流 憂候車人龍會塞爆香港口岸！","createTime":"2019-01-18T15:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T16:27:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bea3708062d2c2b52772c8946af8d852db48c97","tid":986628,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"農曆新年長假將至，港珠澳大橋將首次面對三地春運的「海量」出入境人流挑戰。自大橋通車後，三地口岸多次出現千人排長龍苦候穿梭巴士「金巴」數小時的亂象。為應付新春的客運需求，金巴已預先向跨境直巴公司借用超過三十部旅遊巴，並額外購置二十部新巴士，連同常設巴士合共投放一百八十八部金巴「應戰」。不過，旅遊業界仍不表樂觀，<span style=\"color: red;\">憂慮候車人龍會塞爆香港口岸，促運輸署在口岸分設旅行團及散客候車區域，以防混亂。</span><br />\n<br />\n去年十月通車的港珠澳大橋，交通安排混亂一直為人詬病。金巴營辦商表示，參考其他口岸以往於農曆新年假期期間錄得的跨境旅客數字，預計大橋旅客數目在該段日子將較平日及周末多，因此會加強服務，應付乘客需求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118003033883-0118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fbkn-20190118003033883-0118_00822_001.html&d=CGlvEuLvU3dvRpk9BeDIbwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=3626a0b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118003033883-0118_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1bd4a4090e8cfbda78c7ae1dd58b8164206e2210","tid":986628,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6cf27f58d50ca1b18e0da2ac6e4da9cbfcb5e7","tid":986628,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zaHau7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzaHau7D.jpg&h=ee5179fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bdc9dc63f93c6ab10a45f5c2cab05e843336f9